node.text:
Sometimes I cook! 

ROTEL DIP 🧀🌮
Ground Beef (Seasoned)
Onions
Rotel Tomatoes
Cream Cheese
Velveeta
Shredded Cheese
Tortilla Chips (To Serve)

Brown beef with a little oil and season well. Push to one side of the skillet and add diced onions, Rotel tomatoes, cream cheese, velveeta and shredded cheese. Bake until cheese is melted, mix then serve with tortilla chips. Enjoy!

#tipsybartender #definitelynotgourmet #beef #cheese #marshmallows #nachos #snack #foodie 

@definitelynotgourmet

node.text:
Sometimes I cook! 

ROTEL DIP 🧀🌮
Ground Beef (Seasoned)
Onions
Rotel Tomatoes
Cream Cheese
Velveeta
Shredded Cheese
Tortilla Chips (To Serve)

Brown beef with a little oil and season well. Push to one side of the skillet and add diced onions, Rotel tomatoes, cream cheese, velveeta and shredded cheese. Bake until cheese is melted, mix then serve with tortilla chips. Enjoy!

#tipsybartender #definitelynotgourmet #beef #cheese #marshmallows #nachos #snack #foodie 

@definitelynotgourmet
